The paper deals with a search problem in which tests are carried out on subsets of a set, which is a common theme in information theory (cs.IT), data structures (cs.DS), and discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The use of hypergraphs is also a key aspect of the paper, which is a topic in computational complexity (cs.CC) and social networks (cs.SI).
